          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TRN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A large sample of 239Pu was placed at the 22",
                "and 48 m stations of the BNL fast chopper at beam H2",
                "of the BNL HFBR. With rotor speeds of 2500 and 10000",
                "rev/min, the resonance structure from thermal-neutron",
                "energies to about 50 eV could be observed, with",
                "adequate separation of most of the resonances through",
                "that range."
              ]
            }
